Package TLC.CompilerWhile.ThreeAdresseElements

Class ThreeAdressElement

java.lang.Object
TLC.CompilerWhile.ThreeAdresseElements.ThreeAdressElement
Direct Known Subclasses:
AffecationElement, ArgDeclarationElement, CondElement, ConsElement, ElseElement, ForEachElement, ForElement, FuncCallElement, Function, GotoElement, HdElement, IfElement, IfnzElement, LeftAssignationElement, LeftCondElement, ListElement, NilElement, ReturnElement, RightAssignationElement, RightCondElement, SourceElement, ThenElement, TlElement, VarElement, WhileElement
public abstract class ThreeAdressElement extends Object
This class is an abstract class created to be extended by all the ThreeAdressElements It contains a list of children which will be used to build the ThreeAdressCode It also contains the methods to navigate in the list of children
